《'''法律360'''》（{{lang-en|Law360}}）是一个总部位于[[美国|美国]][[纽约州|纽约州]][[纽约市|纽约市]]的网站<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.bizjournals.com/newyork/news/2016/06/15/non-compete-clauses-come-under-fire-by-n-y.html| title=Non-compete clauses come under fire by N.Y. attorney general| publisher=The Business Journals| date=2016-06-15| access-date=2020-07-13| archive-date=2020-01-26| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126114000/https://www.bizjournals.com/newyork/news/2016/06/15/non-compete-clauses-come-under-fire-by-n-y.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一项[[基于订阅|基于订阅]]（subscription-based）的[[法律|法律]][[新闻|新闻]][[服务|服务]]，由[[律商联讯|律商联讯]]（LexisNexis）<ref name="汪曙华2016">{{cite book|author=汪曙华|title=媒介融合趋势下的出版变迁与转型|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6SGEDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT110|date=2016-12-01|publisher=|isbn=978-7-5657-1846-5|pages=110–}}</ref>的[[子公司|子公司]][[波特弗裡奧传媒|波特弗裡奧传媒]]（Portfolio Media）运营<ref name="KluwerStaff2019">{{cite book|author1=Wolters Kluwer|author2=Wolters Kluwer Editorial Staff|title=Directory of Corporate Counsel, 2020 Edition (2 vols)|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Wm_JDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA1533|date=2019-12-15|publisher=Wolters Kluwer Law & Business|isbn=978-1-5438-1029-5|pages=1533–}}</ref>。该网站由[[马里乌斯·梅兰|马里乌斯·梅兰]] （Marius Meland）和[[马格努斯·霍格隆德|马格努斯·霍格隆德]]（Magnus Hoglund）联合创办<ref>{{cite web| url=https://amlawdaily.typepad.com/amlawdaily/2012/03/lexisnexis-law360.html| title=Simpson Thacher, Wilson Sonsini Advise on Law360's Sale to LexisNexis| publisher=The Am Law Daily| date=2012-03-20| access-date=2020-07-13| archive-date=2021-01-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120223947/https://amlawdaily.typepad.com/amlawdaily/2012/03/lexisnexis-law360.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[域名|域名]]Law360.com<ref name="Hawk2015">{{cite book|author=Barry E. Hawk|title=International Antitrust Law and Policy: Fordham Competition Law 2014|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lar0CQAAQBAJ&pg=PA530|date=2015-03-01|publisher=Juris Publishing, Inc.|isbn=978-1-57823-447-9|pages=530–|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810134034/https://books.google.com/books?id=lar0CQAAQBAJ&pg=PA530|dead-url=no}}</ref>注册于2002年12月27日<ref>{{cite web| url=https://whois.domaintools.com/law360.com| title=Whois Record for Law360.com| work=[[WHOIS|WHOIS]]| accessdate=2020-07-13| archive-date=2020-07-15| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715080145/https://whois.domaintools.com/law360.com| dead-url=no}}</ref>，2003年开始运行。

2003年，《法律360》母公司波特弗裡奧传媒开始出版关于[[知识产权法|知识产权法]]的每日在线新闻<ref name="Talking Biz">{{cite web|url=http://www.talkingbiznews.com/biz-news-help-wanted/law360-seeking-to-hire-reporters-in-new-york/|title=Law360 seeking to hire reports in New York|date=2013-10-07|publisher=talkingbiznews.com|access-date=2020-07-13|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810102658/http://talkingbiznews.com/biz-news-help-wanted/law360-seeking-to-hire-reporters-in-new-york/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2012年，《法律360》被LexisNexis收购<ref>{{cite web | url=https://adage.com/article/btob/lexisnexis-acquires-law360/285868|title=LexisNexis acquires Law360|publisher=adage.com|date=2012-03-21}}</ref>。目前，该机构在美国多地设有新闻处（news bureaus）。

